:1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>漢堡唔使留兩日，漢堡好好住但唔係旅遊城市</blockquote><br />\n咁我我下晝先係柏林去漢堡 留多半日係柏林？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢邊真係唔係好熟 柏林嘅印象都係睇吓歷史"},{"pid":"6b2b2c34486f1b978fd1159d676f015e467c4122","tid":193592,"uid":103232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"巴打去Innsbruck睇水晶？"},{"pid":"5903dc0c0568072a6124c06e71b4b19663d9d9b8","tid":193592,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打去Innsbruck睇水晶？</blockquote><br />\n係呀 朋友話有時間可以去 諗住搭埋纜車上山頂 雖然六月可能冇雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果唔去嘅話我 都係留多日喺慕尼黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43af02f3f1a9d3b6213a42620d56eb49b595db76","tid":193592,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打諗住去邊幾個國家？</blockquote><br />\n德國荷蘭比利時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nInnsbruck係奧地利喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21423baf4ca7aecc4921f8a66d3d0567657a8c8","tid":193592,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打諗住去邊幾個國家？</blockquote><br />\n德國荷蘭比利時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nInnsbruck係奧地利喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我前面仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就同屋企人去 布拉格,CK,Hallstatt,Salzburg,之後國王湖"},{"pid":"680e0a50949ea774a9cd278292fec01e755096f0","tid":193592,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"不過其實水晶又冇乜興趣。最主要都係想睇風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14916b69a43512b4e05634300aa2d703b2efc45","tid":193592,"uid":103232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過其實水晶又冇乜興趣。最主要都係想睇風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nInnsbruck好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去過一次，純粹自駕遊翻慕尼黑經過嘅時候訓一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0507625a1a6182587c55ebd0a065e78a7ae3c5","tid":193592,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過其實水晶又冇乜興趣。最主要都係想睇風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nInnsbruck好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去過一次，純粹自駕遊翻慕尼黑經過嘅時候訓一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見到 人哋上山行山個景幾靚 又有乳牛撚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲以為幾好添 慕尼黑有冇推薦去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa72194822005c6ff51ea09acc1b846af8a843a","tid":193592,"uid":103232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過其實水晶又冇乜興趣。最主要都係想睇風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nInnsbruck好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去過一次，純粹自駕遊翻慕尼黑經過嘅時候訓一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見到 人哋上山行山個景幾靚 又有乳牛撚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲以為幾好添 慕尼黑有冇推薦去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMunich最出名同必去嘅就喺Marienplatz<br />\nNew Town Hall就喺正Marienplatz個個